text: Qendresa Bajra (born 11 May 1992) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Bajra has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:KFF Mitrovica players Category:KFF Hajvalia players
